@startuml

[*] --> Start

state Start
Start : entry / Initialize system
Start : do / Prepare for operations
Start : exit / Ready for input

state AddGoods
AddGoods : entry / Add new items
AddGoods : do / Input item details
AddGoods : exit / Items added to inventory

state UpdatePrice
UpdatePrice : entry / Update item price
UpdatePrice : do / Modify price information
UpdatePrice : exit / Price updated

state RemoveGoods
RemoveGoods : entry / Remove items
RemoveGoods : do / Delete from inventory
RemoveGoods : exit / Items removed

state CheckExpiration
CheckExpiration : entry / Expiry check
CheckExpiration : do / Identify expired items
CheckExpiration : exit / Expired items identified

state PlaceOrder
PlaceOrder : entry / Order placement
PlaceOrder : do / Send order to supplier
PlaceOrder : exit / Order confirmation

state GenerateInvoice
GenerateInvoice : entry / Invoice creation
GenerateInvoice : do / Create invoice document
GenerateInvoice : exit / Invoice generated

state SearchInventory
SearchInventory : entry / Search items
SearchInventory : do / Find available items
SearchInventory : exit / Items found

state CalculateDiscounts
CalculateDiscounts : entry / Discount calculation
CalculateDiscounts : do / Apply discounts and taxes
CalculateDiscounts : exit / Calculations done

state GenerateReceipt
GenerateReceipt : entry / Receipt creation
GenerateReceipt : do / Prepare receipt
GenerateReceipt : exit / Receipt generated

state ReplaceOrCancel
ReplaceOrCancel : entry / Modify receipt
ReplaceOrCancel : do / Update or cancel receipt
ReplaceOrCancel : exit / Action completed

state RecordRequest
RecordRequest : entry / Request handling
RecordRequest : do / Note unavailable items
RecordRequest : exit / Request recorded

state GenerateReport
GenerateReport : entry / Report generation
GenerateReport : do / Compile transaction summary
GenerateReport : exit / Report generated

Start --> AddGoods
AddGoods --> Start
Start --> UpdatePrice
UpdatePrice --> Start
Start --> RemoveGoods
RemoveGoods --> Start
Start --> CheckExpiration
CheckExpiration --> Start
Start --> PlaceOrder
PlaceOrder --> Start
Start --> GenerateInvoice
GenerateInvoice --> Start
Start --> SearchInventory
SearchInventory --> Start
SearchInventory --> CalculateDiscounts
CalculateDiscounts --> Start
CalculateDiscounts --> GenerateReceipt
GenerateReceipt --> Start
GenerateReceipt --> ReplaceOrCancel
ReplaceOrCancel --> Start
Start --> RecordRequest
RecordRequest --> Start
Start --> GenerateReport
GenerateReport --> Start

@enduml
